snippet.title: Cards Of Prophecy - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cards of Prophecy combines Tower Defense, Deckbuilding, and Roguelike elements, with huge inspiration from Trading Card Games. Build an ever evolving deck to summon monsters and use powerful spells. 
Fuse, defend, open card packs, create new strategies. Repeat.
